---
title: Slow-Cooked Chicken Drumstick Risoni with Courgette & Extra Parmesan Cheese
description: Patience is going to be key with this dish. We understand how tempting it is to dig in as soon as possible - it smells so good - but
you’ll be glad for those extra minutes. Allowing the succulent chicken drumsticks to marinate in the creamy stew will add a burst
of flavour to every bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/664fc6ec2ae3a5972f828c70-50b3c2c0.jpeg
